Posted By: James Feagin
Up for sale is the following. All cards have clean backs with no back damage. These cards are paypal only and are first come first serve through e-mail. Since I'm finally becoming a more focused collector, I will ONLY consider cards for trade from the following sets 1933 Tattoo Orbit, 1933 DeLong, 1933 Buttercream, 1933 Uncle Jack's, 1933 George C. Miller. I typically am only trading for Hall of Famers, except for Tattoo Orbit, I'm doing that set. Delivery confirmation is included, but insurance is extra.
Have fun!
